							<a href="#" class="image"><img src="http://res.cloudinary.com/dmj8qtant/image/upload/c_limit,w_600/v1456874247/team_pgyhej.jpg" alt="" data-position="center center" /></a>
							<div class="content">
								<div class="inner">
									<h2>Team</h2>
									<p>Our team was a five-man team of two architecture majors, two landscape architecture majors, and one architectural engineer. The other architect in the group was an exchange student from France. We had a great time working together and learned a lot about the smooth and not-so-smooth parts of interdisciplinary design. Our group name was “The Villagers”, made to connect the team with the general motif in our design work.</p>
								</div>
